A Field to embed QR codes in your cards.

## Usage

To use the QR Code field in your card definitions:

```typescript
import { QRCodeField } from '../fields/qr-code';

@field code = contains(QRCodeField);
```

A typical pattern is to use a computed field that generates the QR code based on the card's ID:

```typescript
@field qrCode = contains(QRCodeField, {
  computeVia: function() {
    return new QRCodeField({data: this.id});
  }
});
```

To display the QR code in your templates:

```handlebars
<@fields.qrCode @format='embedded'/>
```

This field allows you to generate and display QR codes within your cards.
